task.summary: 1.1.160123 ========== * Options window bugs fixed * UI bug fixed + UI language change options added + Web-Search Words/Phrases are now Sent to Cloud * Other bugs fixed
1.1.160123 ========== + Change Download Link to Play Market
1.1.160123 ========== * Change Version and Version Code in Manifest.xml

1.2.160131 ========== + Backup/Restore feature (For Database and Favorites) added * Add Entry UI imporved * Result counter added * Database structure and version changed/updated for future features * Add Entry now more Smart * New-Line bug fixed * DB version changed to 2
1.3.160204 ========== + Greek Alphabet Added + Share text from another application + Added brief exit * Menu rearranged * Bug fixed

1.4.160303 ========== + Synonyms Feature + New entry added in Database * UI improved (Now a lot of space for everything.. ;) ) * "Send to Server" changed to "Report Entry" in Details View * Database improved * Search improved * Bug fixed

1.5.160309 ========== + Synonyms add/edit/change/delete feature added in details view + Help Feature added :) + Favorite feature is now independent. So updating database won't delete favorites (sorry for the previous losses :( ) * UI improved * Bug fixed
